{"tid":891170,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實一個HD係咪一定唔夠","createTime":"2018-11-06T01:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T07:05:31.000Z","uid":152001,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe5756597cf3fa9062058bb54a7523f813bc1b0","tid":891170,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"我依加仲讀緊ive工程 <br />\n本身諗住讀埋依幾個月就出黎做野 <br />\n因為讀書唔算叻 <br />\n但如果唔讀上去又驚第時升唔到職 <br />\n我份intern人工都叫唔錯 雖然都係做狗<br />\n畢左業應該都會係果間做番兩三年 <br />\n但好驚自己做多幾年都仲原地踏步 <br />\n到30歲因爲讀唔夠書而無職升<br />\n其實都有諗過之後再讀番個pt degree<br />\n因為我覺得依加成日讀啲科都好唔實在<br />\n未見過啲機 唔會知佢點運作<br />\n一路做一路學可能會好啲<br />\n我都唔知開係上班台定校園台<br />\n因為其實我都係想問做工程依行 Hd係咪一定唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c0aa9b4b66dfa14cae978712e80bfc04065098","tid":891170,"uid":14261,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"唔好做工程<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"d10f4e865ab1be1af75d956b403b9725170d086d","tid":891170,"uid":94501,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"唔夠 起碼要多個ssd裝windows"},{"pid":"cb6d5cc6ac4009729400e5165667dc35971704da","tid":891170,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d10f4e865ab1be1af75d956b403b9725170d086d","tid":891170,"uid":94501,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"唔夠 起碼要多個ssd裝windows"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe61d213a79c43d8dec50a6be94c5bb4d5bd38f","tid":891170,"uid":152001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6c0aa9b4b66dfa14cae978712e80bfc04065098","tid":891170,"uid":14261,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"唔好做工程<br />\n講完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"聽人講好chur成日ot<br />\n但只係想搵行專啲既黎做<br />\n因為學歷我一定唔夠人鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif